{
  "stem": "11000.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they had set up like Red Cross agencies and so forth, and we went there, and they gave us-- we got rid of our striped clothes.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We got underwear.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We got clothes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They gave us food to eat and so forth.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And don't forget, the war wasn't over until May '45.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is January, so we weren't able to go home yet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we had to stay around, which-- we didn't know when the war was to be over.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the first thing we did when we felt a little bit more strength, we went back to Auschwitz, and although we knew what had happened at the selection, but you still-- you know, you never give up hope.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Yep.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we wanted to see who we know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What about Father?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe some miracle happened, that he was still survive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we looked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We stayed in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I went to-- we went to city hall, and I figure we didn't have any IDs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't have any papers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Nobody knew who we were, what my name is, and so-- I mean, here years have passed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I-- I couldn't even-- I tried a pencil.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I couldn't even write anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was just, you know, things that you take for granted.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You just-- it just isn't there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went to city hall, and we told them that we're from Holland, and we want to go back-- to give us some idea.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The problem was that the Russians used to arrest the Germans on the streets and send them to Russia, to Siberia to work, and we didn't look quite as well as they did, but we were afraid, since we couldn't communicate them, that they took us maybe for different as what we were.",
      "word_count": 53
    }
  ],
